          "text": "1. Overview"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "The stored procedure "
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "USP_AgencyDashboard_MonthlyEnergyUsageRetrieveAgencyCurrentFY",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " is designed to retrieve monthly energy usage data for a specified agency over a rolling 12-month period, defaulting to the current fiscal year. It aggregates energy usage, demand usage, billed amounts, and BTU (British Thermal Units) from a published summary data table, filtered by the agency's hierarchy. The procedure outputs this data along with fiscal year, calendar year, and month information."
        }
